com.ohair.stephen.edp

Class BatchProcessPipeline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ohair.stephen.edp.BatchProcessPipeline

  • public final class BatchProcessPipeline
extends Object
    Pipeline that extracts GSOD records from Google BigQuery and combines them with NexRAD Level II tar files from google storage to create a CSV output file. Runs in batch since the rate at which the data is updated doesn't warrant streaming. Based from the BigQueryTornado[1] and NexRAD[2] examples found on GitHub.
    Author:
    Stephen O'Hair
